commentTextItems.html: driven down to mid-on, Australia win by 7 wickets

commentPostTextItems.html: in the end a comprehensive victory for the visitors
hope you have enjoyed the coverage, be sure to join us on Tuesday for the third and final match of the series
For the latest bulletin on today's play, features and other stories please visit www.cricinfo.com
All feedback about the game and our coverage are welcomed http://www.cricinfo.com/commentary.html
Man of the Match goes to B Lee

commentTextItems.html: turned away on the leg side, scores are level
played down to fine leg, just two more needed now
edged straight through the fielder at first slip, fell short and into the gap between the legs

commentPostTextItems.html: Australia require another 3 runs with 7 wickets and 36 balls remaining
